<br>
a) 60 beast? Old news, I think LoS had one within 72 hrs.<br>
<br>
Well, aside from not being sure (I _know_ one of the big ubers had a 60 in 72 hrs, but am a little fuzzy on which one), I'd assume I got it off LoS's sight.  Who knows, it might have been BotS, Triton, or one of the others too.  I'm too lazy to go look it up now.<br>
<br>
b) Although I don't quite get the point of PLing a class who's only use is for Casual players to solo with....<br>
<br>
Well, looking at the spell lists, they have 2 things to offer the Raid guilds.  Jack and shit.  2nd Tier heals, slows, buffs.  Nothing at all to give someone a reason to bring a BLord over either one of thier parent classes, or a trinity class.  From every account I've read, they are Soloing GODS, something similar to a necro with a hydra cleric.  Thier huge number of shitty quests (much like most of the iksar lower tier ones) all point to the casual/&quot;quester&quot; gamer, as does the solo'ability.<br>
<br>
Of course I could be wrong.  Maybe they'll make a name for themselves for being the suicide Malo class, or DT takers or something....  Or maybe Verant will give them something useful and unique.  It really is too bad BLords can't cast thier pet buffs (not the lvl upping ones obviously) on other pets.  Thats still not Raid calibur, but its a start.<br>
<br>
Ninen of Saryrn<br>
